<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>智能新闻| smithsonianmag.com</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/rss/smart-news/</link><description>智能新闻的 RSS 提要</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 13:22:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>他们的名字已经消失在历史之中。但现在，您可以看到近 2000 年前他们生活在罗马时代城市时的面孔</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/their-names-were-lost-to-history-but-now-you-can-see-what-their-faces-may-have-looked-like-when-they-lived-in-a-roman-era-city-nearly-2000-years-ago-180989179/</link><description>布达佩斯的一个新展览展出了 16 个基于阿昆库姆古城出土头骨的面部重建作品。策展人不知道他们的生活细节，但他们发明了背景故事来填补空白</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/their-names-were-lost-to-history-but-now-you-can-see-what-their-faces-may-have-looked-like-when-they-lived-in-a-roman-era-city-nearly-2000-years-ago-180989179/</guid></item><item><title>视频捕捉到逆戟鲸猛烈撞击翻车鱼导致爆炸的画面。这种神秘的行为可能是一种游戏或青少年照顾的形式</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/video-captures-orcas-ramming-a-sunfish-so-hard-it-explodes-the-mysterious-behavior-might-be-a-form-of-play-or-juvenile-care-180989153/</link><description>在墨西哥加利福尼亚湾记录的两起事件中，逆戟鲸在杀死翻车鱼后共同将这些巨大的动物炸成碎片</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 04:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/video-captures-orcas-ramming-a-sunfish-so-hard-it-explodes-the-mysterious-behavior-might-be-a-form-of-play-or-juvenile-care-180989153/</guid></item><item><title>新研究发现，原住民精神领袖在这个澳大利亚洞穴中进行“魔法、治疗、诅咒”仪式已有 25,000 年之久</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/aboriginal-spiritual-leaders-performed-magic-healing-cursing-rituals-in-this-australian-cave-for-25000-years-new-research-finds-180989178/</link><description>考古学家与古奈库尔奈 (GunaiKurnai) 原住民社区的成员合作，在克洛格斯洞穴 (Cloggs Cave) 内探索了数千年前烧焦草中的灰烬层</description><pubDate>We